 In fogpanel every chargeable resource is a billable item. Fogpanel contain 
pre-built billable item by default for cloud purpose. Admin have option to 
enable and disable it only. If admin want to provide some extra service for
users on month basics. In fogpanel admin use this items option to add the items
for users to provide extra service. In this section contain users recurring and 
custom items for current billing month cycle are listed in grid. Recurring items 
is charged for more than one billing cycle.Custom item is charged for a current month.

